### volume_mount ###
<table border="1" class="nice">
 <thead>
 <tr>
   <th>Field</th>
   <th>Type</th>
   <th>Description</th>
 </tr>
 </thead>
 <tbody>
 <tr>
   <td>container_path</td>
   <td>string</td>
   <td>The path to mount inside the application container</td>
 </tr>
 <tr>
   <td>mode</td>
   <td>string</td>
   <td>Indicates whether the volume should be read-only or read-write</td>
 </tr>
 <tr>
